# PDCA (Plan-Do-Check-Act) Cycle Documentation

Each feature gets a pdca/ subdirectory for tracking the continuous improvement cycle.

Structure:
```
.specify/memory/features/000001-auth-system/pdca/
  plan.md   - Hypothesis and design decisions
  do.md     - Implementation notes and trials
  check.md  - Evaluation and results
  act.md    - Improvements and lessons for next cycle
```
